  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A unique fusion of roulette match-3 and tower defense gameplay!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/df374c3e098a61484571f7b4e9000ab9.poster.avif?t=1740970079\" width=450 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/df374c3e098a61484571f7b4e9000ab9.webm?t=1740970079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Distinctive Match-3 Mechanics:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/be34316d5539aad92094a442966262e0.poster.avif?t=1740970079\" width=450 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/be34316d5539aad92094a442966262e0.webm?t=1740970079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Rotate and switch the roulette to connect units of the same color, merging them into more powerful ones.<br>Each merge not only grants you extra moves but also creates stronger bubbles to fend off enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tower Defense Gameplay:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/a4a82e1aaa99ed7d3559ba07f06032a9.poster.avif?t=1740970079\" width=450 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/a4a82e1aaa99ed7d3559ba07f06032a9.webm?t=1740970079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>But the challenge doesn’t stop there! You’ll need to carefully plan your merges and precisely position the roulette to ensure your units can aim at the enemies effectively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/3657754fc4fdb357fc7be073f07ffc59.poster.avif?t=1740970079\" width=450 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/3657754fc4fdb357fc7be073f07ffc59.webm?t=1740970079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your moves run out, enemies will charge toward the core, and your merged units will fire bullets to stop them from advancing! Each round of defense will test your strategy and skills as you protect the roulette and hold the final line of defense!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A unique fusion of roulette match-3 and tower defense gameplay!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/df374c3e098a61484571f7b4e9000ab9.poster.avif?t=1740970079\" width=450 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/df374c3e098a61484571f7b4e9000ab9.webm?t=1740970079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Distinctive Match-3 Mechanics:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/be34316d5539aad92094a442966262e0.poster.avif?t=1740970079\" width=450 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/be34316d5539aad92094a442966262e0.webm?t=1740970079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Rotate and switch the roulette to connect units of the same color, merging them into more powerful ones.<br>Each merge not only grants you extra moves but also creates stronger bubbles to fend off enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tower Defense Gameplay:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/a4a82e1aaa99ed7d3559ba07f06032a9.poster.avif?t=1740970079\" width=450 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/a4a82e1aaa99ed7d3559ba07f06032a9.webm?t=1740970079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>But the challenge doesn’t stop there! You’ll need to carefully plan your merges and precisely position the roulette to ensure your units can aim at the enemies effectively.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/3657754fc4fdb357fc7be073f07ffc59.poster.avif?t=1740970079\" width=450 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3490690/extras/3657754fc4fdb357fc7be073f07ffc59.webm?t=1740970079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When your moves run out, enemies will charge toward the core, and your merged units will fire bullets to stop them from advancing! Each round of defense will test your strategy and skills as you protect the roulette and hold the final line of defense!</p>",
